BOCI APP is a comprehensive mobile application developed by BOCI Securities Co., Ltd. This mobile app provides Hong Kong and USA stock market data information, market hot news, securities trading function, online account opening and social platform to users.

[Hong Kong & USA stock market] BOCI APP provides users with basic quotes for Hong Kong stocks and a 15-minute delay in US stocks to help customers catch up every investment opportunity;

[Hot News] Users can obtain global hot news information at BOCI APP and catch up with the market trend;

[Securities Trading] BOCI APP offers users a security and reliable trading channels, all trading orders will be process directly to Hong Kong Stock Exchange, US stock exchange and Shanghai and Shenzhen Stock Exchanges;

[Online account opening] BOCI APP provides users with a one-stop account opening experience with online submission, users may choose face-to-face account opening and non-face-to-face account opening;

[Social Function] BOCl APP provides users an interactive communication and experience sharing platform.

